<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #d9534f;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d9534f;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c9302c;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
        .logo-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo-container">
            <a href="#">
                <img style="width: 70px;" id="logo"
                     src="https://tiptop-stag.syd1.digitaloceanspaces.com/staging/TipTopDriver.png"
                     width="70" alt="" />
            </a>
        </div>

        
        <p>Dear {{driverName}},</p>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>We hope this message finds you well. We wanted to inform you that your TipTop Cabby account is currently inactive because your required documents have expired.</p>
            
            <h2>What You Need to Do:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Update Your Documents:</strong> Please upload the updated versions of your {{documentTypes}} as soon as possible.</li>
                <li><strong>Verification Process:</strong> Once you’ve submitted the updated documents, our team will review them promptly. You’ll receive a confirmation email when your account is reactivated.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>How to Update:</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Log in to the TipTop Cabby app.</li>
                <li>Go to the "Documents" section under your profile.</li>
                <li>Upload the necessary documents and submit them for verification.</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p>We understand the inconvenience, and we’re here to help you through this process. If you need any assistance, please don’t hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your prompt attention to this matter. We look forward to having you back on the road with TipTop Cabby!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The TipTop Cabby Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message; please do not reply to this email. If you have any questions, contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
